<p></p><div class="folderlabel" onclick="togglefolder('folder13');">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Web Originals&nbsp;</div><div id="folder13" class="folder" isfolder="true" style="display:block;">
<ul><li> Appears in <em><a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Literature/SailorNothing" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Literature/SailorNothing">Sailor Nothing</a></em>, where <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/MadArtist" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/MadArtist">Argon</a> targets <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/AlphaBitch" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/AlphaBitch">an unpleasant classmate that every one of the heroes had a reason to hate</a> and used her as the object of a lesson in what constitutes <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/CardCarryingVillain" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/CardCarryingVillain">true Evil</a> rather than mere pettiness.
